<plot>Two teams compete in a super-advanced game of charades. The people playing the game move at seemingly impossible speed, solving long clues based on puns. An approximate example: Would a man who has two stains on his shirt from different pieces of chicken subscribe to the two pullet theory?" Imagine being able to solve this charade in under a minute. The show was popular in Canada in the mid-seventies, and featured Billy Van from Sonny and Cher, the Bobby Vinton Show, etc...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581499</url></doc>
